t; At 55 don’t chase runners, they will come back on their own, without friends – but if you chase it you will argo everthing. <br>2&gt; At 55 from the wooden platform you can pull any named mob, by its self.<br>3&gt; Depreds are SK’s and HT so watch out.<br>4&gt; Keep your Resist Magic up at all times, your stuns don’t recharge fast enough to stop a lot of the casters.<br>5&gt; If the Chief spawns with a knife in its right hand, that’s the sticker, If its left hand is blinking red then it has the Essence, when you don’t see ether of them it has your idol.<br><br>I hope this will help my brother and Sisters not to make the same mistake I did, and make it a lot safer camp.<br><br>May Tunare smile on your quests. <br> <p><table border=0>  <tr><td><img src="http://kickim.tripod.com/Fantasy/sword.gif">    </td><td>Beldukil Lawbringer<br> Level 59 Knight of Tunare<br>Grey Council<br>        Povar<br>    </td><td><img src="http://kickim.tripod.com/Fantasy/sword.gif"></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showPrevMessage?topicID=43.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showNextMessage?topicID=43.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=43.topic><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.emailToFriend?topicID=43.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.threadControl?topicI